Definition: completely satisfactory
Example: his smile said that everything was copacetic; You had to be a good judge of what a man was like, and the English was copacetic- John O'Hara
Synonyms: copasetic, copesetic, copesettic, completely, satisfactory, his, smile, said, that, everything, was, You, had, to, be, a, good, judge, of, what, man, like, and, the, English, -, John, O, Hara
Category: adj.all
